# Pyenc

# Install

````
pkg up -y
````

````
pkg i python -y
````

````
pip install pyenc
````

# Run

````
pyenc
````


Use Letest Termux Version 0.118.0 (118) : <a href="https://f-droid.org/repo/com.termux_118.apk">DOWNLOAD TERMUX v118</a>
